# Angular Service Rules

- Use services to wrap `web-serial-rxjs` usage.
- Keep services responsible for connection, send, receive, and error stream orchestration.
- Expose read-only Observables or Signals to components.
- Do not expose writable Subjects.
- Keep service APIs small and example-friendly.
